            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/naturalvoice/" class=" " title="晴雨表">晴雨表</a>
                (自然而然)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="17579650">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">夜深人静独坐观心，始觉妄穷而真独露，常于此中得大机趣；既觉真现而妄难逃，又于此中得大惭愧。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-04-01 14:04</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>夜深人静独坐观心，始觉妄穷而真独露，常于此中得大机趣；既觉真现而妄难逃，又于此中得大惭愧。</q></blockquote>
